        "@value": "\n        \nMénestrel with guest artist Vincent Lauzer\n\n \nSat, Nov 14, 2026 @ 7:30 pm\nRosthern, SK – @ Station Arts Centre Cooperative\nPresented by Station Arts Centre Cooperative\n\n\n\n\nSavour the tradition of the troubadours, as Ménestrel breathes vivid life into music that has been shaped by centuries. Their voyage through historic repertoire is accented by lute, guitar and the intricate colours of the human voice. With selections ranging from grand compositions by Purcell, Dowland, and Monteverdi to nostalgic Gaelic, Québécois, and English folk melodies, Ménestrel reminds us of the pleasure of these musical forms. The group consists of recognized artists Janelle Lucyk (soprano), Kerry Bursey (tenor, guitar and lute) and Vincent Lauzer (recorder). who have established a reputation for combining ancient repertoire with elements of folk song.\n\n\nClassical\n\nWatch Video:\n\nAppearances\n\n\n\n\n\nFri, Nov 13, 2026 @ 7:30 pm\n\n\nBuy Tickets\n\n\n\nTisdale, SK - Maurice Taylor Performing Arts Theatre\n\nPresented by Tisdale Arts Council\n\n\n\n\n\nSat, Nov 14, 2026 @ 7:30 pm\n\n\n\n\n\nRosthern, SK - Station Arts Centre Cooperative\n\nPresented by Station Arts Centre Cooperative\n\n\n\n\n\nWed, Nov 18, 2026 @ 7:30 pm\n\n\nBuy Tickets\n\n\n\nBiggar, SK - Majestic Theatre\n\nPresented by Biggar & District Arts Council\n\n\n\n\n\nThu, Nov 19, 2026 @ 7:30 pm\n\n\n\n\n\nLuseland, SK - Luseland Homecoming Hall\n\nPresented by Luseland Arts Council\n\n\n\n\n\nFri, Nov 20, 2026 @ 7:30 pm\n\n\nBuy Tickets\n\n\n\nKindersley, SK - Norman Ritchie Community Centre\n\nPresented by Kindersley & District Arts Council\n\n\n\n\n\nSat, Nov 21, 2026 @ 7:30 pm\n\n\n\n\n\nSwift Current, SK - Event Centre\n\nPresented by Swift Current Arts Council\n\n\n\n\n\nTue, Nov 24, 2026 @ 7:30 pm\n\n\nBuy Tickets\n\n\n\nAssiniboia, SK - Prince of Wales Cultural & Recreation Centre\n\nPresented by Assiniboia & District Arts Council\n\n\n\n\n\nWed, Feb 3, 2027 @ 7:30 pm\n\n